Name: zoneinfo_dir
Type: STRING
Default-Value: NULL
Last-Modified: 3.13.1

The absolute path to the zoneinfo directory, containing timezone
definitions as generated by the vzic tool.  This overrides any compile-time
value that was set with the **--with-zoneinfo-dir** configure option.

If not specified, and no compile-time value was set, then whatever
definitions libical finds will be used.

If you are providing a Time Zone Data Distribution Service (i.e. you have
"tzdist" listed in *httpmodules*), then this configuration option
or a compile time value MUST be specified. 
